data.description: This brick home has a nice flowing floor plan with a spacious one bedroom apartment downstairs.  Entrance from inside as well as private entry/parking for the apartment.  Tiled and hardwood floors, fireplace, vaulted ceilings, dining/office/media room off the living room.  Fenced back yard with deck. 20x30 shop with electric and plumbing. Back yard is gated and has driveway for additional parking.
